info.name: /move
info.description: Move all the members from a channel to another. If you select a category channel, all the users from all the voice channels inside the category will be moved.
examples: /move #Gameplay #Party - Move all the members from the channel `Gameplay` to the channel `Party`.
/move #Voice Channels #Web Churras - Move all the members from all the channels of the category `Voice Channels` to the channel `Web Churras`.
/move 922257017828175942 913499995985047612 - Move all the members from the channel of ID `922257017828175942` to the channel of ID `913499995985047612`.
